    <presenter back="Welcome" displayOrder="3" menuLabel="Instructions" type="text" self="Instructions" title="Instruksen">
        <plainText featureText="Wetem aplikasen ia yu save makem rikoding blong lanwis blong yu, bambai ol pipol blong Vanuatu mo ol pipol blong evri ples long world save harem lanwis blong yu. I gat fulap foto blong difren ples long Malakula wea i stap insaed long aplikasen ia. Bai yu showem ol foto ia long wan olfala woman o wan olfala man blong vilej blong yu mo askem long hem se i tokabaot ol foto ia long lanwis blong hem. Yu save transletem wanem i talem, tu."/>
